# TaskFlow Terminology & Style Guide

## Product Terminology

**Always use these terms consistently:**

- **Workspace** - The top-level container (NOT "Project" at the top level)
- **Project** - Collections of related tasks within a Workspace
- **Task** - Individual work items (NOT "To-do" or "Item")
- **Epic** - Large features spanning multiple tasks
- **Cycle** - Our 2-week iteration period (NOT "Sprint")
- **Activation** - When a user completes key setup steps (NOT "Onboarding completion")
- **Member** - Individual user in a Workspace (NOT "User" in product copy)

